---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 1, 2024';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Beautyflow Beauty Salon"
  description="Beautyflow Beauty Salon's privacy policy. Learn how we handle your personal data."
  lang="en"
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#fdf8f6] via-white to-[#f8f4f9]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase text-center font-bold">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">1. Data Controller</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Name:</strong> Beautyflow Kft.<br />
            <strong>Address:</strong> 1116 Budapest, Fegyvernek utca 121., Hungary<br />
            <strong>Tax number:</strong> 32724316-1-43<br />
            <strong>Company registration:</strong> 01-09-439280<br />
            <strong>Email:</strong> hello@beautyflow.pro<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +36 1 300 9414
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We collect and process the following personal data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Name (first name, last name)</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Treatment interest (type of service)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">3. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Establishing contact and providing callbacks</li>
            <li>Scheduling consultation appointments</li>
            <li>Responding to customer service inquiries</li>
            <li>Providing information about our services</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">4. Legal Basis</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The legal basis for data processing is your consent (GDPR Article 6(1)(a)),
            which you provide by completing and submitting the consultation form.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">5. Data Retention Period</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We store personal data until the inquiry is processed, but for a maximum of 2 years,
            unless you request deletion earlier.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">6. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We do not share your data with third parties, except for the following service providers
            who provide technical support for data processing:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Resend</strong> - Email delivery service</li>
            <li><strong>Google Sheets</strong> - Data storage (servers within the EU)</li>
            <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> - Website hosting</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Right of access:</strong> Request information about your stored data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to rectification:</strong> Request correction of your data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li><strong>Data portability:</strong> Request your data in a machine-readable format</li>
            <li><strong>Right to object:</strong> Object to data processing</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">8. Contact and Complaints</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            For privacy-related questions or complaints, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@beautyflow.pro" class="text-[#c53f75] underline">hello@beautyflow.pro</a>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            If you believe your rights have been violated, you may file a complaint with the
            Hungarian National Authority for Data Protection and Freedom of Information (NAIH):<br />
            <strong>Address:</strong> 1055 Budapest, Falk Miksa utca 9-11., Hungary<br />
            <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://naih.hu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[#c53f75] underline">naih.hu</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">9. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our website uses essential cookies required for basic functionality.
            These cookies do not collect personal data for marketing purposes.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a
          href="/en/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#c53f75] text-white font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide rounded-full hover:bg-[#a33460] transition-colors"
        >
          Back to Homepage
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
